title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E77 - Clash at Daxio
description: The Pit Crew joins Brian Wayne Foster to discuss all the behind-the-scenes secrets! Later on, Matt Mercer, Liam O'Brien, and Marisha Ray join to discuss the latest episode.
